#USAGE : 
perl <(curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cpanelsky/PostMig/master/domainstats.pl) -help

   Options:
     -help   -> This!
     -ipdns  -> Check http status, IP's, DNS IP's
     -hosts  -> Show suggested /etc/hosts file
     -mail   -> Check for email accounts
     -all    -> All the things!


